<plot>In a London hotel room, Len tries to come to terms with his failed marriage and a relationship with a 17 year old prostitute, Dory. The impending arrival of his wife and Dory's refusal to leave is a moving backdrop to a fundamental dilemma in Len's life: 'the daughter that never was.' Intimate Strangers is a desperate search for comfort and solace where lovers and daughters are confusingly linked.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?267394</url></doc>
